n.</pos> <conjf>Laming</conjf>.]</vmorph> <def>To make lame.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>If you happen to let child fall and <qex>lame</qex> it.</q>
<rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>lamedh</ent>⟦br⟧
